  </section>

  <!-- ── GUARANTEE / HOW IT WORKS ── -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="bg-[#5D4FE0]/5 border border-[#5D4FE0]/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink leading-snug mb-3">How The Ranking Atlas Guarantee Works</h3>
        <p class="text-base text-[#475569] leading-relaxed mb-3">Most digital PR agencies charge monthly retainers with no link guarantees. You pay for their time and hope for the best. We do the opposite.</p>
        <p class="text-base text-[#475569] leading-relaxed mb-3">Every Ranking Atlas campaign costs $3,500. That's the price whether we deliver 8 links or 15. We keep running story angles — reactive PR, expert commentary, data campaigns — until a minimum of 8 earned placements are secured. If a campaign overdelivers, you don't pay more. If it takes longer than expected, we keep working at no additional cost.</p>
        <p class="text-base text-[#475569] leading-relaxed mb-6">No retainers. No rolling contracts. One campaign, one price, a guaranteed minimum outcome. Most campaigns deliver 8–12+ placements across publications with real editorial standards and real audiences.</p>
