        Be The Brand <span class="relative inline-block pb-2">AI Recommends<svg viewBox="0 0 200 12" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-full h-3" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 8 Q 50 2, 100 6 T 198 5" stroke="white" stroke-width="3" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>.
